natural_language_question: Which patients have received a diagnosis of I10?
query:
PREFIX sphn: <https://www.biomedit.ch/rdf/sphn-schema/sphn/>  
PREFIX icd: <https://www.biomedit.ch/rdf/sphn-schema/sphn/icd#>  

SELECT ?patient WHERE {  
  ?patient sphn:hasDiagnosis ?diag .  
  ?diag sphn:hasCode ?code .  
  ?code sphn:hasCodeValue icd:I10 .  
}

Question: What patients are over the age of 41?
Answer Example 0: PREFIX sphn: <https://www.biomedit.ch/rdf/sphn-schema/sphn/>
SELECT ?patient WHERE {
  ?patient sphn:hasBirthDate ?dob .
  BIND(year(NOW()) - year(?dob) AS ?age)
  FILTER(?age >= 41)
}


Example 1:
Question: Which patients have been diagnosed with I427?
Answer Example 1: PREFIX sphn: <https://www.biomedit.ch/rdf/sphn-schema/sphn/>
PREFIX icd: <https://www.biomedit.ch/rdf/sphn-schema/sphn/icd#>

SELECT ?patient WHERE {
  ?patient sphn:hasDiagnosis ?diag .
  ?diag sphn:hasCode ?code .
  ?code sphn:hasCodeValue
         icd:I427 .
}


Example 2:
Question: Which patients have taken M01AE01?
Answer Example 2: PREFIX sphn:  <https://www.biomedit.ch/rdf/sphn-schema/sphn/>
SELECT ?patient WHERE {
  ?presc sphn:hasSubjectPseudoIdentifier> ?patient .
  ?presc sphn: ?drug .
  ?drug sphn:hasCode ?code .
  ?code sphn:hasValue "M01AE01"
}
